{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["Centaur and the Port \"Elders\"\n\n<size=45>Chapter 5 - Centaur's Image<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"You've managed to attain everything I've ever wished for in life... Oh, how I envy you...","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":207020},{"expression":4,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Oh, r- really...?","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.2,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":206040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"say":"Envying the youth is not a good look for you, Ark Royal.","dir":1,"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":207040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"But that's everything I've ever wanted!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"effects":[{"active":true,"name":"speed"}],"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":207020},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ah! Good morning, Elder Victorious!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"effects":[{"active":false,"name":"speed"}],"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":206040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Morning. Here's my mission report, Commander. Please look it over.","dir":1,"side":2,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Look over the report."}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":207040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"My, upon closer inspection, I sense a sort of familiarity about you, Centaur. Why, I dare say with a change of clothes you could very well pass for me.","actor":207040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"You think so too, Victorious? I'm glad I'm not the only one...","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":207020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"You're in good spirits again! ...But are you sure this isn't just some psychological by-product of your jealousy?","actor":207040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Absolutely not! It's more that this air of familiarity emanating from Centaur has me wanting to get closer to her... at which point we can address the prior issue...","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"action":[{"type":"shake","y":0,"delay":1,"dur":0.4,"number":2,"x":22.5}],"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":207020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"All right then.","actor":207040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"say":"To be honest, I feel the same familiarity from both of you, Elders.","actor":206040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Do you now? What say we leave this silly old biddy behind and go for a spot of tea? We have much to discuss.","actor":207040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Commander, would you mind lending me your secretary for a tick?","dir":1,"side":0,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Nod in agreement."}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":207040},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"side":2,"say":"......","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Now Centaur, your appearance here truly is unique. Take these ears, for example, are they as real as Duke of York's?","actor":207040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Indeed. Actually, I was somewhat surprised when I noticed I was a bit different from my Elders.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":206040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"That's true. They're not even like the animal ears on the Sakura girls. Really something special.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":207020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":2,"time":0.5},"say":"Any idea why that is, Commander?","dir":1,"side":2,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Shake your head negatively."}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":207020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Um, while I don't fully understand it myself, from time to time, I do get a sort of foggy image that comes to mind...","actor":206040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"say":"Oh? And what is it?","dir":1,"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":207040},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Might it have something to do with my name? A centaur is a mythological creature from deep in the forest, after all.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":206040},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Perhaps that forms an association in the collective consciousness with the race of forest-dwelling Elves...?","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":206040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"\"Collective consciousness...?\" That sounds like the kind of thing Akashi and Yuubari are always on about.","actor":207020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Elder Akashi and Elder Yuubari? I'll have to be sure to ask them about it next time I see them.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":206040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"So these ears truly are as mysterious as Duke of York's... Anyway, these fantastical clothes of yours are very much my style. You'll have to let me look at them so I can make myself a set.","actor":207040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"That would be fine...","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":206040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Now I have some matters to attend to. ――Commander, I'm returning your secretary.","actor":207040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I should be going as well. But Centaur, the next time you play with the destroyer girls, why don't you, um, well, invite me along...?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"action":[{"type":"shake","y":0,"delay":1.5,"dur":0.4,"number":2,"x":22.5}],"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":207020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Certainly! Thank you very much, Elders!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":206040,"bgName":"bg_story_task","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"BANRENMA5","fadeOut":1.5}